{"word":"ἐποκέλλω","slug":"ἐποκέλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐποκέλλω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ἐπικέλλω'><el>ἐπικέλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to run</i> a ship <i>ashore</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of the ship, <i>to run aground</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}